Montastic,is,an,online,site,and,server,monitoring,service,When,your,services,go,down,or,become,unreachable,for,some,reason,Montastic,will,alert,you,through,an,email,when,the,services,are,down,and,again,when,they,are,restored,Monitoring,frequency,is,up,to,every,minutes,paid,Montastic,will,check,URLs,through,a,mixture,of,HTTP,HEAD,and,GET,requests,depending,on,what,s,most,appropriate,The,RESTful,Montastic,API,allows,rd,party,developers,the,opportunity,to,integrate,Montastic,services,directly,into,their,own,applications,Checkpoint,info,creation,deletion,listing,and,editing,methods,are,all,included,in,the,API